Package org.planit.output.configuration

Class OriginDestinationOutputTypeConfiguration

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.planit.output.configuration.OutputTypeConfiguration
      • org.planit.output.configuration.OriginDestinationOutputTypeConfiguration
  • public class OriginDestinationOutputTypeConfiguration
extends OutputTypeConfiguration
    The configuration for the origin-destination output type. The following OutputProperty values are included by default:
    • RUN_ID
    • TIME_PERIOD_EXTERNAL_ID
    • MODE_EXTERNAL_ID
    • ORIGIN_ZONE_EXTERNAL_ID
    • DESTINATION_ZONE_EXTERNAL_ID
    • OD_COST
    Author:
    markr
